{"tid":1474756,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港人從未如此重要過","createTime":"2019-08-15T09:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T11:21:29.000Z","uid":127479,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"da6b0571057c7acbf239c6d959913b06c98aad88","tid":1474756,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:39:03.000Z","msg":"此刻大家都很憤怒，我也很憤怒，但現在卻是最需要清醒及智慧的時候，因為侵侵正式將香港抗爭帶進中美區隔的大戰略之中。現在已不是單純反對一條移交逃犯條例的地區事，而是大國鬥爭的高層次事宜。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>「籌碼」與「棋子」是兩個截然不同的事物，前者是不會隨便送給對方，而後者隨時可以被放棄。香港究竟會成為美國一個重要籌碼，還是一個用完即棄的棋子，決定權全在香港人手中。</span>香港人的一個行動或決定，將影響中美兩個大國的對抗局面，甚至影響歷史走向。百多年來，香港人從未如此重要過。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n大家已無須關注四點警察記招或林鄭說什麼，眼睛應往遠方望。<span style=\"color: orange;\">此刻美國援軍已到，切入點不一樣，玩法也不一樣。切入點不再是林鄭，而是美國政府，對象亦不再侷限於殘暴的警渣</span>，而是解放軍現在用一個口號概括的話，就如附圖那樣。<br />\n<br />\n「不在前線就沒有發言權」及「一切讓前線決定」等資格論，是反送中無大台式抗爭的優點，但同時也是其缺點。在機場示威中，我們都看到中共使出污髒的手段意圖構陷前線抗爭者，但我們只能站在一旁當觀眾，看著中共奸計得呈。<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">然而現在層次而上升至大國鬥爭，真不容許再墮入中共圈套了。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我衷心希望前線抗爭者能夠看遠一點，殘暴的警渣不會一天就消失，留著自己的性命，總有一天他們要還債。<br />\n<br />\n（Donald Trump決定叉隻腳入嚟，其實喺想轉移焦點，事關美國國內經濟衰退嘅陰霾愈來愈濃。其實佢仲有反口空間，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>為免佢將香港變成佢一隻隨時可棄嘅棋子，香港人就要夾佢上呢隻船，要沉就一齊沉！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n史健仁Facebook <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果侵可以保住香港、做低邪惡軸心、阻止中共出兵香港，佢仲唔名留青史，輕鬆連任？今次侵可以Make America great again，又點會咁易放棄機會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82262d41c421b9b6889077435af3deea266f859f","tid":1474756,"uid":127479,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8hwgRhS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8hwgRhS.jpg&h=310f8d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n漏咗幅圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd65dcfd001dc29981eba911ad94de1bc57fb49","tid":1474756,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9b309ee89bdc0421bda3b6a573e38e26877265","tid":1474756,"uid":16374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKtyThf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKtyThf.png&h=d5bda484&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddadbc8239fd5294beaa456e637fe9ef75527c6e","tid":1474756,"uid":298833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:50:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e7b3ca784eefc7547c3d30ce33d2581867d8e44","tid":1474756,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:44:24.000Z","msg":"It's a war now<br />\n需要步步為營"},{"pid":"30dc8e8b7ff7557be23806689bedf91630ec436b","tid":1474756,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:45:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beabaa77e61fbeb1b4e4cbcbbe365136d280dc96","tid":1474756,"uid":127479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825ad8524b6c8e70e4df1310df8de2c91374e313","tid":1474756,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:11:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JeaEPyr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJeaEPyr.png&h=b7f80800&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94dd6be96e9197755f3562891a4ff5d1b0be29d9","tid":1474756,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:12:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">NOW OR NEVER</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m7YruyT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"h